1029
00:52:18,794 --> 00:52:21,126
Crush? Really?

1030
00:52:21,163 --> 00:52:25,827
OK, Crush. I need to
the East Australian Current.

1031
00:52:25,868 --> 00:52:27,096
E.A.C.?

1032
00:52:27,136 --> 00:52:29,070
Oh, dude.

1033
00:52:29,105 --> 00:52:31,471
You're ridin' it, dude!

1034
00:52:31,507 --> 00:52:34,135
Check it out!

1035
