She is sub-level, dude.

1045
00:53:35,171 --> 00:53:37,731
Dory! Dory! Dory!

1046
00:53:37,773 --> 00:53:39,502
Dory.

1047
00:53:41,243 --> 00:53:44,076
I'm so sorry.

1048
00:53:44,113 --> 00:53:47,446
This is all my fault.
It's my fault.

1049
00:53:47,483 --> 00:53:52,453
Twenty-nine, thirty!
Ready or not, here I come!

1050
00:53:52,454 --> 00:53:54,479
There you are!

1051
00:53:58,661 --> 00:54:01,027
Dory?

1052
00:54:01,063 --> 00:54:02,894
Nice wave!

1053
00:54:06,702 --> 00:54:08,536
Up you go!

1054
