1064
00:54:49,111 --> 00:54:51,011
Jellyman, offspring.

1065
00:54:51,046 --> 00:54:53,105
Offspring, Jellyman.

1066
00:54:53,148 --> 00:54:56,675
- Jellies?! Sweet.
- Totally.

1067
00:54:56,719 --> 00:54:59,950
Apparently, I must've done
something you liked... dudes.

1068
00:54:59,989 --> 00:55:02,423
You rock, dude!

1069
