to the big ol' blue.

1074
00:55:14,470 --> 00:55:16,802
- All by themselves?
- Yeah.

1075
00:55:16,839 --> 00:55:19,831
But, dude, how do you know
when they're ready?

1076
00:55:19,875 --> 00:55:21,103
Well, you never really know.

1077
00:55:21,143 --> 00:55:24,544
But when they know,
you'll know, you know? Ha.

1078
00:55:28,784 --> 00:55:30,217
Hey, look, everybody.

1079
