- No way.
- What happened?

1092
00:55:58,747 --> 00:56:00,908
No, no, kids.
I don't want to talk about it.

1093
00:56:00,950 --> 00:56:03,282
Aww! Please?

1094
00:56:03,319 --> 00:56:04,650
Please?

1095
00:56:04,687 --> 00:56:07,422
Well, OK.

1096
00:56:07,423 --> 00:56:11,257
