1145
00:58:22,257 --> 00:58:23,588
Gill?

1146
00:58:26,061 --> 00:58:27,790
Gill?

1147
00:58:27,830 --> 00:58:30,492
Hey, Sharkbait.

1148
00:58:30,532 --> 00:58:32,762
I'm sorry I couldn't stop the...

1149
