1152
00:58:40,476 --> 00:58:43,912
I was willing to put you
in harm's way to get there.

1153
00:58:43,946 --> 00:58:47,905
Nothing should be worth that.

1154
00:58:47,950 --> 00:58:51,181
I'm sorry I couldn't get you
back to your father, kid.

1155
00:58:54,890 --> 00:58:57,791
All right. Hey, hey, hey...

1156
00:58:57,826 --> 00:58:59,453
What the...

1157
00:58:59,495 --> 00:59:03,226
That's one way to pull a tooth.

1158
00:59:03,265 --> 00:59:05,358
Darn kids.

1159
00:59:05,400 --> 00:59:08,392
Good thing I pulled the
right one, eh, Prime Minister?

1160
00:59:08,437 --> 00:59:09,995
Hey.

1161
00:59:10,038 --> 00:59:12,029
Oh, Nigel!
You just missed an extraction.

1162
00:59:12,074 --> 00:59:14,702
Has he loosened
the periodontal ligament yet?

1163
00:59:14,743 --> 00:59:16,802
What am I talking about?
Where's Nemo?

1164
00:59:16,912 --> 00:59:19,176
- I've got to speak with him.
- What is it?

1165
00:59:19,214 --> 00:59:21,307
Your dad's been fighting
the entire ocean...

1166
