Some sort of sport fish.

1170
00:59:33,362 --> 00:59:35,523
- Tuna? Trout?
- Marlin?

1171
00:59:35,564 --> 00:59:37,395
Marlin! The little clownfish
from the reef.

1172
00:59:37,432 --> 00:59:40,026
It's my dad!
He took on a shark!

1173
00:59:40,068 --> 00:59:42,400
I heard he took on three.

1174
00:59:42,437 --> 00:59:45,270
