like a maniac.

1177
00:59:49,711 --> 00:59:51,076
Really?

1178
00:59:51,113 --> 00:59:52,910
He's swimming,
giving it all he's got...

1179
00:59:52,948 --> 00:59:55,007
and then three gigantic
sharks capture him...

1180
00:59:55,050 --> 00:59:57,314
and he blows them up
and dives thousands of feet...

1181
00:59:57,352 --> 01:00:00,185
and gets chased by a monster
with huge teeth!

1182
01:00:00,222 --> 01:00:02,850
He ties this demon to a rock,
and what's his reward?

1183
01:00:02,891 --> 01:00:05,257
He gets to battle
an entire jellyfish forest!

1184
01:00:05,294 --> 01:00:08,491
Now he's with a bunch of
sea turtles on the E.A. C...

1185
01:00:08,530 --> 01:00:12,022
