this way right now... to Sydney!

1186
01:00:12,067 --> 01:00:13,432
What a good daddy!

1187
01:00:13,468 --> 01:00:16,028
He was looking for you
after all, Sharkbait.

1188
01:00:19,541 --> 01:00:21,168
He's swimming to the filter!

1189
01:00:21,210 --> 01:00:22,700
- Sharkbait!
- Not again!

1190
01:00:24,246 --> 01:00:27,181
Sharkbait!

1191
01:00:27,216 --> 01:00:28,581
No!

1192
01:00:28,617 --> 01:00:29,811
You got your whole life
ahead of you!

1193
01:00:29,851 --> 01:00:32,251
