- Get him out!

1194
01:00:36,558 --> 01:00:38,219
Get him out of there!

1195
01:00:38,260 --> 01:00:39,887
Come on, kid! Grab the end!

1196
01:00:39,928 --> 01:00:42,522
Sharkbait!

1197
01:00:42,564 --> 01:00:44,589
- No!
- Can you hear me?

1198
01:00:44,633 --> 01:00:46,123
Nemo! Can you hear me?

1199
01:00:46,168 --> 01:00:48,193
Yeah, I can hear you.

1200
01:00:48,237 --> 01:00:50,171
Sharkbait, you did it!

1201
01:00:50,205 --> 01:00:54,005
Sharkbait, you're...
covered with germs!

1202
01:00:54,042 --> 01:00:56,110
That took guts, kid.

1203
01:00:56,111 --> 01:00:58,602
All right, gang,
we have less than 48 hours...

1204
01:00:58,647 --> 01:00:59,944
