1205
01:00:59,982 --> 01:01:01,677
This tank'll get
plenty dirty in that time...

1206
01:01:01,717 --> 01:01:04,550
but we have to help it along
any way we can.

1207
01:01:04,586 --> 01:01:06,850
- Jacques? No cleaning.
- I shall resist.

1208
01:01:06,888 --> 01:01:09,550
Everybody else,
be as gross as possible.

1209
01:01:09,591 --> 01:01:10,819
Think dirty thoughts.

1210
01:01:10,859 --> 01:01:13,054
We're gonna make
this tank so filthy...

1211
01:01:13,095 --> 01:01:15,620
